{"tid":1778694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國眾議員約霍: manufacture anywhere but China","createTime":"2019-12-11T06:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T18:08:48.000Z","uid":47352,"like":430,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"5d3e838ebab6437fad73bf737d467a8fc457b937","tid":1778694,"uid":47352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:51:43.000Z","msg":"美國聯邦眾議院外交委員會亞太小組選在國際人權日這天，針對中國境內政治、宗教人權挑戰舉行聽證會，聚焦新疆再教育營及香港「反送中」示威等議題。擔任眾院外委會亞太小組共和黨首席議員的約霍（Ted Yoho）表示，外界無法主宰中國，也無法強迫中國做任何事，因此需要透過制度化所謂的「製造ABC政策」，向中國與製造商傳遞清楚訊息。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n約霍解釋，「製造ABC政策」指的是「除了中國，哪裡製造都行」（manufacture anywhere but China），因為中國目前所作所為靠的都是金錢。約霍指出：「我們無法強迫他們（中國）做任何事，但我們毫無疑問地能夠對製造商施以公眾壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n談及中國在全球的觸角，約霍表示，他在上屆美國國會擔任亞太小組主席期間，曾與台灣方面人員會晤，會前他的幕僚接到中國大使電話，表達不希望他與台方會面。他說：「你們能想像嗎？我身為美國國會議員<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">，卻接到中方電話要我不能出席會議。我告訴對方：『管好你自己的事，我要見誰就見誰』。」</span></span>"},{"pid":"9c4fc79a3e2ba1d9e3542a6f32a9b420e58f93ac","tid":1778694,"uid":249263,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:00:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美加議員講對華政策，<br />\n響task2 急要人</span></span><br />\n適逢人權日，世界上人權被打壓嘅國家或地區唔少，當然其中一個亮點係打壓緊香港同新疆嘅中國！<br />\n<br />\n多國政要發推文關注中國打壓人權嘅情況，精選推文遍布task 1 &amp; 2，大家快啲去回應啦！<br />\n<br />\n記得落hashtag #humanrights #HumanRightsDay 呀～<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwg1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=0c2605e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"83bdf5e0093816db430b0a3411b532401df8b766","tid":1778694,"uid":296369,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:01:30.000Z","msg":"Anywhere but China......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ca8cec9c614b8f1566082580000cfdec838adf","tid":1778694,"uid":68463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587216872d550483e49df29de8954c7c632d4347","tid":1778694,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:04:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02c7abe0cf794b56f265d28bdec78a3889e5cc34","tid":1778694,"uid":165683,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:05:06.000Z","msg":"全球黃色經濟圈"},{"pid":"ce5e2457138c3379af1be393d199d8ad5cdd4b17","tid":1778694,"uid":188176,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:05:07.000Z","msg":"Yoho: Go fuck yourself<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9336520714e1e82f19076eb5f79820d390e9ecc","tid":1778694,"uid":9151,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:06:16.000Z","msg":"支那弱智到 成班禽獸用動物角度去同人類打交道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5162c5256bfbf225389ac60df3b2abf509be2af5","tid":1778694,"uid":1589,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:06:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">管好你自己的事，我要見誰就見誰</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65abb8a4266ae2dd03645f90eb5c012a61daa29c","tid":1778694,"uid":149662,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:07:10.000Z","msg":"粗暴干預內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94fb5ff962fcd08658fb